-1 PUNISHMENTS~
Multiplaying:
  Each character multiplaying will be slain, and the corpse eaten.
Exploiting bugs: 
  First offense: Slay.
  Further offenses: Banning.
Spamming public channels: 
  Nochanneling.  Frequent offenders will be banned or frozen. 
Sexual harrasment:
  On public channels: Punishment may range from nochannel up to deletion
                      dependent on frequency.
  Person-to-person: Verbal warning from immortals, then freezing 
                    up to banning/deletion.
Cussing on channels other than flame: 
  Verbal warning, nochanneling for frequent offenders. 
NonPK assisting in a pk-event: 
  NonPKer slain/munched, then forced pk.
Dispelling in safe: 
  Verbal warning, possible slay or another punishment for frequent offenders.
Bots: 
  1st Offense: slay  2nd Offense: deny
Bringing an agressive mob to a player:
  Slay/munch.
Bringing a player to an agressive mob:
  Slay/munch.  

PK-Specific Rules:

Ordering your opponent to kill a sure-kill mob: 
  Slay/munch.
SpamWhining about losing: 
  Nochanneling
Killing a truly link-dead character: 
  Slay/munch.
Stealing eq from a corpse:
  Slay/munch.
